[{"title":"Hello Everyone","url":"/captured77/2025/01/10/hello-everyone/","content":""},{"title":"LCR-152 判断二叉搜索树","url":"/captured77/2025/01/12/Leetcode/152-verify-bst/","content":"<h1 id=\"题目描述\"><a href=\"#题目描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h1><p>请实现一个函数来判断整数数组postorder是否为二叉搜索树<strong>后续遍历</strong>的结果.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/captured77/image/bst-01.png\" alt=\"s\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"题解\"><a href=\"#题解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题解\"></a>题解</h1><p><strong>后续遍历的定义:</strong> 左子树&gt; 右子树 &gt; 根节点</p>\n<p><strong>二叉搜索树:</strong> 左子树所有节点的值 &lt; 根节点的值;右子树中所有的节点的值&gt; 根节点的值;左右子树也是二叉搜索树</p>\n<h1 id=\"递归分治\"><a href=\"#递归分治\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"递归分治\"></a>递归分治</h1><p><strong>递归解析:</strong> 终止条件,当i&gt;&#x3D;j ,说明此子树的节点数量&lt;&#x3D;1,无需判断正确性,因此直接返回true.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>划分左右子树:  遍历后续遍历的[i,j]区间,寻找<strong>第一个大于根节点</strong>的节点,索引记为m,.此时,可划分出左右子树区间[i,m-1],此时, 可以划分出左子树区间[m,j-1],根节点索引j</li>\n<li>判断是否为二叉搜索树:<ol>\n<li>左子树区间: [i,m-1]内所有节点都应&lt;postoder[j].而划分左右子树区间已经保证了左子树区间的正确性,因此判断右子树区间即可</li>\n<li>右子树区间: [m, j-1]内的所有节点都应 &gt; postorder[j]实现方式遍历,当遇到&lt;&#x3D; postorder[j]的节点跳出;则可通过p&#x3D;j,判断是否为二叉搜索树.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>返回值: 所有子树都正确才判定正确, 因此使用逻辑符 &amp;&amp; 连接</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h1><figure class=\"highlight golang\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">verifyTreeOrder</span><span class=\"params\">(postorder []<span class=\"type\">int</span>)</span></span> <span class=\"type\">bool</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> dfs <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span><span class=\"params\">(i, j <span class=\"type\">int</span>)</span></span> <span class=\"type\">bool</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    dfs = <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span><span class=\"params\">(i, j <span class=\"type\">int</span>)</span></span> <span class=\"type\">bool</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> i &gt;=j &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        p := i </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> postorder[p] &lt; postorder[j] &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            p++</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        m := p </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> postorder[p] &gt; postorder[j] &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            p++</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> p == j &amp;&amp; dfs(i, m<span class=\"number\">-1</span>) &amp;&amp; dfs(m, j<span class=\"number\">-1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>  dfs(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(postorder)<span class=\"number\">-1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["算法"],"tags":["Leetcode"]},{"title":"ubuntu22.04国内源部署docker","url":"/captured77/2025/01/10/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/docker-ubuntu-deploy/","content":"<ul>\n<li><p>更新包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>安装依赖包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt install apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl gnupg lsb-release</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>添加阿里云Docker镜像源GPG秘钥</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -fsSL https://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu/gpg | <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/docker-archive-keyring.gpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>添加阿里云镜像源</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;deb [arch=amd64 signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/docker-archive-keyring.gpg] https://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu <span class=\"subst\">$(lsb_release -cs)</span> stable&quot;</span> | <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> <span class=\"built_in\">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list &gt; /dev/null</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>查看docker-ce 版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-cache madison docker-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>安装指定版本的docker-ce</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt-get install docker-ce=5:23.0.2-1~ubuntu.22.04~jammy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>启动docker 服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl start docker &amp;&amp; systemctl <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>查看docker服务</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl status docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>docker 配置普通用户</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> groupadd docker  <span class=\"comment\"># 添加用户组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> gpasswd -a username docker <span class=\"comment\">#将当前用户添加到用户组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">newgrp docker          <span class=\"comment\"># 更新用户组</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","categories":["部署相关"],"tags":["docker部署"]}]